{
  "stem": "23832.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they threw them out into the ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] when-- if you wanted to take a jacket before they take you, you go to the closet to reach for it, they'd have shot you.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So people just left the way they had things on them and that's all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I don't know if I told I told you, there was no soap.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You see, it came to a point that we didn't have soap.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, I had some, but those who were thrown into the ghetto, they couldn't take with think of soap when they couldn't think of anything more important.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That which they wore came apart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were sitting around-- I not to forget [? your ?] a situation-- sitting around the ones on the sidewalk that you see sometimes homeless, that's what it is.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when you had a brown bag, like I have now, with something in it, they called them the catchers or the snatchers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would snatch it because they hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, in one situation, you're not going to believe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what they did, they wanted to show the world how bad we are, that we are so bad.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was dressed like with a hat, and decent, like you dress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would-- these [NON-ENGLISH], I told you-- they would go and pick you from the street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had to take-- you see, the starvation was big.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And who dies most?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The parents, and their children are not alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know, because their bodies need more food or because they feel pity for the children and give their bite to them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know the reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So, they die first.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
